  <brief_title>The Effect of Broccoli Sprout Extract and Probiotics for Eradication of Helicobacter Pylori</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Broccoli Sprout Extract and Probiotics on Proton Pump Inhibitor-based Triple Therapy for Eradication of Helicobacter Pylori: a Prospective Randomized Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
